title: Garmin City Navigator Australia and New Zealand NT 2013.20 Mapso
description:
Garmin City Navigator Australia and New Zealand NT 2013.20 Mapsource Unlocked


Install the package with the CNNZAUNAVNT2013_20Update.msi file, the setup will install BaseCamp and MapInstall too: replace the original exes with the patched ones.

Maps are already unlocked.

Complete unlocked IMG map included.
Unlocked 3D Buildings file included.
Junction View (JCV) file included.
ASR, G2S, DB file included.

Mapsource v6.16.3 original installer included.
Mapsource v6.16.3 patched exe included.
BaseCamp v3.3.3.0 patched exe included.
MapInstall v4.0.1 patched exe included.

Complete unlocked IMG map can be viewed on the PC, copy it on an USB drive (Garmin folder) and start BaseCamp.


Have fun !!
